        <section id="site-name">
            <h2>Site Name</h2>
            <p><strong>Green Thumb Community Garden</strong></p>
            <p>This name was chosen because it reflects the mission of fostering gardening skills ("green thumb") while emphasizing community and wellness through urban gardening.</p>
            <p><em>Optional domain availability:</em> greenthumbgarden.org</p>
        </section>

        <section id="site-purpose">
            <h2>Site Purpose</h2>
            <p>This website serves as a hub for urban gardeners, volunteers, and wellness advocates by providing:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Information on community gardening benefits (food access, sustainability, mental health)</li>
                <li>Volunteer opportunities and plot rental details</li>
                <li>Educational resources (seasonal planting guides, composting, mindfulness exercises)</li>
                <li>Event schedules and therapeutic gardening sessions</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="scenarios">
            <h2>Scenarios (User Questions)</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>"How can I volunteer at the community garden?"</li>
                <li>"What are the mental health benefits of gardening?"</li>
                <li>"Where can I find local planting guides for beginners?"</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section id="color-schema">
            <h2>Color Schema</h2>
            <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #4a8f29;">
                <p><strong>Primary Green (#4A8F29)</strong> - Used for headings, buttons, and accents</p>
            </div>
            <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #ccc;">
                <p><strong>Light Gray (#F5F5F5)</strong> - Background for sections and cards</p>
            </div>
            <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #333; color: white;">
                <p><strong>Dark Text (#333)</strong> - Body text for readability</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="typography">
            <h2>Typography</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Headings:</strong> "Montserrat" (Google Fonts) - Clean and modern</li>
                <li><strong>Body Text:</strong> "Open Sans" (Google Fonts) - Readable and friendly</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

